fields.title: bella VersaBrew 2-in1 Coffee Maker, Fits-anywhere Kitchenware, Brew 3 Sizes Carafes & Single Serve Cups, Dishwasher Safe Reusable Filter & Filter Holder, Iced Coffee Function, 60oz Tank, Oatmilk
fields.description:
Brew Your Way: Enjoy the flexibility of brewing an instant single-serve cup in 8oz, 10oz, or 12oz sizes with grounds or pods, or brew a full 12-cup carafe. The bella VersaBrew 2-in-1 Coffee System offers customized coffee options for any craving

Fits-Anywhere Design: With a slim profile, this automatic coffee machine is part of our Fits-anywhere kitchenware system, saving up to 50% more space and tucking neatly under most cabinets, making it compatible with any kitchen setup and decor

Customizable Brewing Height: Our k cup coffee maker features an adjustable drip tray that fits travel mugs up to 7” tall, ensuring mess-free brewing whether you’re making a quick single-serve or filling a larger mug for your busy morning commute

Keep Warm & Consistent: The warming plate of our electric pot keeps your 12-cup carafe hot for up to 2 hours, while the carafe lid’s mixing tube ensures a consistent blend with every pour. Perfect for those who like to sip throughout the morning

Easy to Clean: With dishwasher-safe parts like the carafe, filter, and filter holder, cleaning up the express coffee machine is a breeze. The 61oz removable water reservoir makes refills simple, keeping your coffee maker ready for the next brew
